ifferent. A map might appear as a treatise, a spell text as a ledger page or another spell, and so on. Confuse languages and explosive runes can be cast on the secret page, but comprehend languages does not reveal the true contents. The caster may reveal the real page by command word, read it, and return it to secret form. Repeating the command word twice removes the spell. Others detecting faint magic may try dispel magic, but failure destroys the page. Short of alter reality or wish, only will-o-wisp or boggart essence reveals the page’s true nature without dispel magic. Material Component: Powdered herring scales.","notes":"","link":"","class":"Magic-User"},"magic user secret page":{"name":"Secret Page","level":"3","school":"Alteration","range":"Touch","duration":"Until dispelled","aoe":"One page up to 2 square feet","components":"V, S, M","ct":"1 turn","save":"None","save_type":"","description":"Secret Page\n\nSchool: Alteration\nLevel: 3\nComponents: V, S, M\nRange: Touch\nCasting Time: 1 turn\nDuration: Until dispelled\nSaving Throw: None\nArea of Effect: One page up to 2 square feet\nThis spell changes a page’s apparent contents into something entirely different. A map might appear as a treatise, a spell text as a ledger page or another spell, and so on. Confuse languages and explosive runes can be cast on the secret page, but comprehend languages does not reveal the true contents. The caster may reveal the real page by command word, read it, and return it to secret form. Repeating the command word twice removes the spell. Others detecting faint magic may try dispel magic, but failure destroys the page. Short of alter reality or wish, only will-o-wisp or boggart essence reveals the page’s true nature without dispel magic. Material Component: Powdered herring scales.","notes":"","link":"","select_value":"Magic-User: Secret Page","class":"Magic-User"},"sepia snake sigil":{"name":"Sepia Snake Sigil","level":"3","school":"Conjuration/Summoning","range":"½”","duration":"Special","aoe":"One sigil","components":"V, S, M","ct":"3 segments","save":"None","save_type":"","description":"Sepia Snake Sigil\n\nSchool: Conjuration/Summoning\nLevel: 3\nComponents: V, S, M\nRange: ½”\nCasting Time: 3 segments\nDuration: Special\nSaving Throw: None\nArea of Effect: One sigil\nThis spell has three forms, each eventually conjuring a deep brown snake-like force. The sepia snake springs into being and attacks the nearest living creature, but not the caster. It attacks as a monster with Hit Dice equal to the caster’s level. On a hit, the victim is engulfed in a shimmering amber field of force, frozen and immobilized until released by the caster or freed by dispel magic. Nothing can reach or move the victim while enclosed. If the snake misses, it dissipates in a flash of brown light, a loud noise, and a 1” puff of dun-colored smoke lasting 1 round. The three applications are: a glowing sigil drawn in the air and pointed at the target; an umber glyph marked on a surface that is touched or viewed; or a small character written into a magical work to protect it. Material Components: 100 gp worth of powdered amber, a snake scale, and a pinch of mushroom spores.","notes":"","link":"","class":"Magic-User"},"magic user sepia snake sigil":{"name":"Sepia Snake Sigil","level":"3","school":"Conjuration/Summoning","range":"½”","duration":"Special","aoe":"One sigil","components":"V, S, M","ct":"3 segments","save":"None","save_type":"","description":"Sepia Snake Sigil\n\nSchool: Conjuration/Summoning\nLevel: 3\nComponents: V, S, M\nRange: ½”\nCasting Time: 3 segments\nDuration: Special\nSaving Throw: None\nArea of Effect: One sigil\nThis spell has three forms, each eventually conjuring a deep brown snake-like force. The sepia snake springs into being and attacks the nearest living creature, but not the caster. It attacks as a monster with Hit Dice equal to the caster’s level. On a hit, the victim is engulfed in a shimmering amber field of force, frozen and im