:"Mordenkainen’s Lucubration","level":"6","school":"Alteration","range":"0","duration":"Instantaneous","aoe":"The magic-user","components":"V, S","ct":"1 segment","save":"None","save_type":"","description":"Mordenkainen’s Lucubration\n\nSchool: Alteration\nLevel: 6\nComponents: V, S\nRange: 0\nCasting Time: 1 segment\nDuration: Instantaneous\nSaving Throw: None\nArea of Effect: The magic-user\nThis spell allows the magic-user to instantly recall one spell they memorized, cast, and forgot within the past 24 hours. The recalled spell cannot be higher than 5th level. The recalled spell returns exactly as if it had never been cast and can be cast normally on a later round. If the recalled spell requires material components, those components must be available or the spell cannot be used until they are obtained.","notes":"","link":"","class":"Magic-User"},"magic user mordenkainen s lucubration":{"name":"Mordenkainen’s Lucubration","level":"6","school":"Alteration","range":"0","duration":"Instantaneous","aoe":"The magic-user","components":"V, S","ct":"1 segment","save":"None","save_type":"","description":"Mordenkainen’s Lucubration\n\nSchool: Alteration\nLevel: 6\nComponents: V, S\nRange: 0\nCasting Time: 1 segment\nDuration: Instantaneous\nSaving Throw: None\nArea of Effect: The magic-user\nThis spell allows the magic-user to instantly recall one spell they memorized, cast, and forgot within the past 24 hours. The recalled spell cannot be higher than 5th level. The recalled spell returns exactly as if it had never been cast and can be cast normally on a later round. If the recalled spell requires material components, those components must be available or the spell cannot be used until they are obtained.","notes":"","link":"","select_value":"Magic-User: Mordenkainen’s Lucubration","class":"Magic-User"},"transmute water to dust":{"name":"Transmute Water To Dust","level":"6","school":"Alteration","range":"6”","duration":"Permanent","aoe":"1 cubic “ per caster level","components":"V, S, M","ct":"6 segments","save":"None and special","save_type":"","description":"Transmute Water To Dust\n\nSchool: Alteration\nReversible: Transmute Dust To Water\nLevel: 6\nComponents: V, S, M\nRange: 6”\nCasting Time: 6 segments\nDuration: Permanent\nSaving Throw: None and special\nArea of Effect: 1 cubic “ per caster level\nThis spell is identical to the 6th-level druid spell of the same name, except as noted above. The magic-user does not need mistletoe as a material component.\n\nMagic-User Spells, 7th Level","notes":"","link":"","class":"Magic-User"},"magic user transmute water to dust":{"name":"Transmute Water To Dust","level":"6","school":"Alteration","range":"6”","duration":"Permanent","aoe":"1 cubic “ per caster level","components":"V, S, M","ct":"6 segments","save":"None and special","save_type":"","description":"Transmute Water To Dust\n\nSchool: Alteration\nReversible: Transmute Dust To Water\nLevel: 6\nComponents: V, S, M\nRange: 6”\nCasting Time: 6 segments\nDuration: Permanent\nSaving Throw: None and special\nArea of Effect: 1 cubic “ per caster level\nThis spell is identical to the 6th-level druid spell of the same name, except as noted above. The magic-user does not need mistletoe as a material component.\n\nMagic-User Spells, 7th Level","notes":"","link":"","select_value":"Magic-User: Transmute Water To Dust","class":"Magic-User"},"banishment":{"name":"Banishment","level":"7","school":"Abjuration/Evocation","range":"2”","duration":"Permanent","aoe":"2 levels or Hit Dice of creatures per caster level","components":"V, S, M","ct":"7 segments","save":"Special","save_type":"","description":"Banishment\n\nSchool: Abjuration/Evocation\nLevel: 7\nComponents: V, S, M\nRange: 2”\nCasting Time: 7 segments\nDuration: Permanent\nSaving Throw: Special\nArea of Effect: 2 levels or Hit Dice of creatures per caster level\nThis spell forces one or more creatures from another plane to return to their own plane. The effect is instantaneous, and the subject cannot return without special summoning or some other means of travel from its plane. More than one creature can be banished if the caster has enough levels to affect their combined levels or Hit Dice and if the targets are within range. The caster must name the creature type, give the true and proper name, and call upon powers opposed to the creature. The target’s magic resistance must be overcome for the spell to work. The material components are substances harmful, hateful, or opposed to the subject. Each such substance imposes -2 on the target’s saving throw. For example, iron, holy water, sunstone, and rosemary used against a demon impose a -8 saving throw penalty. Special items, such as ki-rin tail hair or couatl feathers, may increase this to -3 or -4 per item; weaker opposed items, such as a devil’s scale, titan’s hair, or druid-blessed mistletoe used against a demon, may impose only -1. If the subject saves, backlash energy deals 2d6 damage to the caster and stuns the caster for 2d6 segments. If the powers invoked are directly and actively opposed to the creature, or actively favor the caster’s interests, they may improve component effectiveness by -1 to -6, at the referee’s judgment.","notes":"","link":"","class":"Magic-User"},"magic user banishment":{"name":"Banishment","level":"7","school":"Abjuration/Evocation","range":"2”","duration":"Permanent","aoe":"2 levels or Hit Dice of creatures per caster level","components":"V, S, M","ct":"7 segments","save":"Special","save_type":"","description":"Banishment\n\nSchool: Abjuration/Evocation\nLevel: 7\nComponents: V, S, M\nRange: 2”\nCasting Time: 7 segments\nDuration: Permanent\nSaving Throw: Special\nArea of Effect: 2 levels or Hit Dice of creatures per caster level\nThis spell forces one or more creatures from another plane to return to their own plane. The effect is instantaneous, and the subject cannot return without special summoning or some other means of travel from its plane. More than one creature can 