sion":{"name":"Detect Illusion","level":"1","school":"Divination","range":"Touch","duration":"3 rounds + 2 rounds per level","aoe":"Line of sight, 1” wide and 1” per level long","components":"V, S, M","ct":"1 segment","save":"None","save_type":"","description":"Detect Illusion\n\nSchool: Divination\nLevel: 1\nComponents: V, S, M\nRange: Touch\nCasting Time: 1 segment\nDuration: 3 rounds + 2 rounds per level\nSaving Throw: None\nArea of Effect: Line of sight, 1” wide and 1” per level long\nThis spell allows the illusionist to see an illusion and know it for exactly what it is. The caster may also let another creature see the illusion as unreal by touching that creature with both hands while it looks at the illusion. Material Component: A piece of yellow-tinted crystal, glass, or mica.","notes":"","link":"","select_value":"Illusionist: Detect Illusion","class":"Illusionist"},"illusionist detect invisibility":{"name":"Detect Invisibility","level":"1","school":"Divination","range":"1” per level","duration":"5 rounds per level","aoe":"1” path","components":"V, S, M","ct":"1 segment","save":"None","save_type":"","description":"Detect Invisibility\n\nSchool: Divination\nLevel: 1\nComponents: V, S, M\nRange: 1” per level\nCasting Time: 1 segment\nDuration: 5 rounds per level\nSaving Throw: None\nArea of Effect: 1” path\nExcept as noted above, this spell is the same as the 2nd-level magic-user spell detect invisibility.","notes":"","link":"","select_value":"Illusionist: Detect Invisibility","class":"Illusionist"},"illusionist gaze reflection":{"name":"Gaze Reflection","level":"1","school":"Alteration","range":"0","duration":"1 round","aoe":"Special","components":"V, S","ct":"1 segment","save":"None","save_type":"","description":"Gaze Reflection\n\nSchool: Alteration\nLevel: 1\nComponents: V, S\nRange: 0\nCasting Time: 1 segment\nDuration: 1 round\nSaving Throw: None\nArea of Effect: Special\nThis spell creates a mirror-like area of air before the illusionist. Any gaze attack, such as that of a basilisk or medusa, is reflected back upon the gazer if it looks at the spellcaster.","notes":"","link":"","select_value":"Illusionist: Gaze Reflection","class":"Illusionist"},"gaze reflection":{"name":"Gaze Reflection","level":"1","school":"Alteration","range":"0","duration":"1 round","aoe":"Special","components":"V, S","ct":"1 segment","save":"None","save_type":"","description":"Gaze Reflection\n\nSchool: Alteration\nLevel: 1\nComponents: V, S\nRange: 0\nCasting Time: 1 segment\nDuration: 1 round\nSaving Throw: None\nArea of Effect: Special\nThis spell creates a mirror-like area of air before the illusionist. Any gaze attack, such as that of a basilisk or medusa, is reflected back upon the gazer if it looks at the spellcaster.","notes":"","link":"","class":"Illusionist"},"illusionist hypnotism":{"name":"Hypnotism","level":"1","school":"Enchantment/Charm","range":"3”","duration":"1 round + 1 round per level","aoe":"One to six creatures","components":"V, S","ct":"1 segment","save":"Negates","save_type":"","description":"Hypnotism\n\nSchool: Enchantment/Charm\nLevel: 1\nComponents: V, S\nRange: 3”\nCasting Time: 1 segment\nDuration: 1 round + 1 round per level\nSaving Throw: Negates\nArea of Effect: One to six creatures\nThe illusionist’s gestures and droning incantation make 1d6 creatures susceptible to a later suggestion. The suggestion is not part of the spell itself and must be spoken after hypnotism is cast. Creatures that save are not affected.","notes":"","link":"","select_value":"Illusionist: Hypnotism","class":"Illusionist"},"hypnotism":{"name":"Hypnotism","level":"1","school":"Enchantment/Charm","range":"3”","duration":"1 round + 1 round per level","aoe":"One to six creatures","components":"V, S","ct":"1 segment","save":"Negates","save_type":"","description":"Hypnotism\n\nSchool: Enchantment/Charm\nLevel: 1\nComponents: V, S\nRange: 3”\nCasting Time: 1 segment\nDuration: 1 round + 1 round per level\nSaving Throw: Negates\nArea of Effect: One to six creatures\nThe illusionist’s gestures and droning incantation make 1d6 creatures susceptible to a later suggestion. The suggestion is not part of the spell itself and must be spoken after hypnotism is cast. Creatures that save are not affected.","notes":"","link":"","class":"Illusionist"},"illusionist light":{"name":"Light","level":"1","school":"Alteration","range":"6”","duration":"1 turn per level","aoe":"2” radius globe","components":"V, S","ct":"1 segment","save":"None","save_type":"","description":"Light\n\nSchool: Alteration\nLevel: 1\nComponents: V, S\nRange: 6”\nCasting Time: 1 segment\nDuration: 1 turn per level\nSaving Throw: None\nArea of Effect: 2” radius globe\nThis spell is the same as the 1st-level magic-user spell light.","notes":"","link":"","select_value":"Illusionist: Light","class":"Illusionist"},"illusionist phantom armor":{"name":"Phantom Armor","level":"1","school":"Alteration/Illusion","range":"Touch","duration":"Special","aoe":"One person","components":"V, S, M","ct":"1 round","save":"None","save_type":"","description":"Phantom Armor\n\nSchool: Alteration/Illusion\nLevel: 1\nComponents: V, S, M\nRange: Touch\nCasting Time: 1 round\nDuration: Special\nSaving Throw: None\nArea of Effect: One person\nThis spell creates a quasi-real suit of plate mail around the subject. It protects as plate mail, AC 3, unless an opponent actively disbelieves it, or unless it is removed by dispel illusion, dispel magic, or a wand of negation. The armor absorbs 1 point of damage per caster level from attacks that would otherwise hit AC 3. Once that damage is absorbed, the armor vanishes. Remaining damage and later damage affect the wearer normally. The spell also grants +1 on saving throws against attack forms similarly affected by magic armor. It does not hinder movement or spellcasting and does not function with other magical protection. Material Component: A small mithral plate worth 10 gp, consumed by the spell.","notes":"","link":"","select_value":"Illusionist: Phantom Armor","class":"Illusionist"},"phantom armor":{"name":"Phantom Armor","level":"1","school":"Alteration/Illusion","range":"Touch","duration":"Special","aoe":"One person","components":"V, S, M","ct":"1 round","save":"None","save_type":"","description":"Phantom Armor\n\nSchool: Alteration/Illusion\nLevel: 1\nComponents: V, S, M\nRange: Touch\nCasting Time: 1 round\nDuration: Special\nSaving Throw: None\nArea of Effect: One person\nThis spell creates a quasi-real suit of plate mail around the subject. It protects as plate mail, AC 3, unless an opponent actively disbelieves it, or unless it is removed by dispel illusion, dispel magic, or a wand of negation. The armor absorbs 1 point of damage per caster level from attacks that would otherwise hit AC 3. Once that damage is absorbed, the armor vanishes. Remaining damage and later damage affect the wearer normally. The spell also grants +1 on saving throws against attack forms similarly affected by magic armor. It does not hinder movement or spellcasting and does not function with other magical protection. Material Component: A small mithral plate worth 10 gp, consumed by the spell.","notes":"","link":"","class":"Illusionist"},"illusionist phantasmal force":{"name":"Phantasmal Force","level":"1","school":"Illusion/Phantasm","range":"6” + 1” per level","duration":"Special","aoe":"4 square inches + 1 square inch per level","components":"V, S, M","ct":"1 segment","save":"Special","save_type":"","description":"Phantasmal Force\n\nSchool: Illusion/Phantasm\nLevel: 1\nComponents: V, S, M\nRange: 6” + 1” per level\nCasting Time: 1 segment\nDuration: Special\nSaving Throw: Special\nArea of Effect: 4 square inches + 1 square inch per level\nExcept as noted above, this spell is the same as the 3rd-level magic-user spell phantasmal force.","notes":"","link":"","select_value":"Illusionist: Phantasmal Force","class":"Illusionist"},"illusionist read illusionist magic":{"name":"Read Illusionist Magic","level":"1","school":"Divination","range":"0","duration":"2 rounds per level","aoe":"Special","components":"V, S, M","ct":"1 segment","save":"None","save_type":"","description":"Read Illusionist Magic\n\nSchool: Divination\nReversible: Yes\nLevel: 1\nComponents: V, S, M\nRange: 0\nCasting Time: 1 segment\nDuration: 2 rounds per level\nSaving Throw: None\nArea of Effect: Special\nThis spell functions like read magic, but applies only to illusionist spells and inscriptions written in illusionist-style magical script.","notes":"","link":"","select_value":"Illusionist: Read Illusionist Magic","class":"Illusionist"},"read illusionist magic":{"name":"Read Illusionist Magic","level":"1","school":"Divination","range":"0","duration":"2 rounds per level","aoe":"Special","components":"V, S, M","ct":"1 segment","save":"None","save_type":"","description":"Read Illusionist Magic\n\nSchool: Divination\nReversible: Yes\nLevel: 1\nComponents: V, S, M\nRange: 0\nCasting Time: 1 segment\nDuration: 2 rounds per level\nSaving Throw: None\nArea of Effect: Special\nThis spell functions like read magic, but applies only to illusionist spells and inscriptions written in illusionist-style magical script.","notes":"","link":"","class":"Illusionist"},"illusionist spook":{"name":"Spook","level":"1","school":"Illusion/Phantasm","range":"0","duration":"Special","aoe":"One creature within 1”","components":"V, S","ct":"1 segment","save":"Negates","save_type":"","description":"Spook\n\nSchool: Illusion/Phantasm\nLevel: 1\nComponents: V, S\nRange: 0\nCasting Time: 1 segment\nDuration: Special\nSaving Throw: Negates\nArea of Effect: One creature within 1”\nThis spell plays upon the subject’s natural fears. The illusionist advances threateningly, and if the subject fails its saving throw, it turns and flees in the opposite direction as if affected by a wand of fear, though it does not drop carried items. A phantasm from the victim’s own mind seems to pursue it. Each round after the first, the victim receives another saving throw, with a cumulative +1 bonus each round, until the spell is broken. The spell affects only creatures with Intelligence 1 or higher.","notes":"","link":"","select_value":"Illusionist: Spook","class":"Illusionist"},"spook":{"name":"Spook","level":"1","school":"Illusion/Phantasm","range":"0","duration":"Special","aoe":"One creature within 1”","components":"V, S","ct":"1 segment","save":"Negates","save_type":"","description":"Spook\n\nSchool: Illusion/Phantasm\nLevel: 1\nComponents: V, S\nRange: 0\nCasting Time: 1 segment\nDuration: Special\nSaving Throw: Negates\nArea of Effect: One creature within 1”\nThis spell plays upon the subject’s natural fears. The illusionist advances threateningly, and if the subject fails its saving throw, it turns and flees in the opposite direction as if affected by a wand of fear, though it does not drop carried items. A phantasm from the victim’s own mind seems to pursue it. Each round after the first, the victim receives another saving throw, with a cumulative +1 bonus each round, until the spell is broken. The spell affects only creatures with Intelligence 1 or higher.","notes":"","link":"","class":"Illusionist"},"illusionist wall of fog":{"name":"Wall Of Fog","level":"1","school":"Alteration","range":"3”","duration":"2d4 rounds + 1 round per level","aoe":"Special","components":"V, S, M","ct":"1 segment","save":"None","save_type":"","description":"Wall Of Fog\n\nSchool: Alteration\nLevel: 1\nComponents: V, S, M\nRange: 3”\nCasting Time: 1 segment\nDuration: 2d4 rounds + 1 round per level\nSaving Throw: None\nArea of Effect: Special\nThis spell creates a wall of misty vapors within range. The fog obscures all sight, including infravision, beyond 2 feet. The area is a cube 2” on each side per caster level. The vapors persist for at least 3 rounds unless blown away by a strong breeze. Material Component: A pinch of split dried peas.","notes":"","link":"","select_value":"Illusionist: Wall Of Fog","class":"Illusionist"},"wall of fog":{"name":"Wall Of Fog","level":"1","school":"Alteration","range":"3”","duration":"2d4 rounds + 1 round per level","aoe":"Special","components":"V, S, M","ct":"1 segment","save":"None","save_type":"","description":"Wall Of Fog\n\nSchool: Alteration\nLevel: 1\nComponents: V, S, M\nRange: 3”\nCasting Time: 1 segment\nDuration: 2d4 rounds + 1 round per level\nSaving Throw: None\nArea of Effect: Special\nThis spell creates a wall of misty vapors within range. The fog obscures all sight, including infravision, beyond 2 feet. The area is a cube 2” on each side per caster level. The vapors persist for at least 3 rounds unless blown away by a strong breeze. Material Component: A pinch of split dried peas.\n\nIllusionist Spells, 2nd Level","notes":"","link":"","class":"Illusionist"},"illusionist alter self":{"name":"Alter Self","level":"2","school":"Alteration/Illusion","range":"0","duration":"3d4 rounds + 2 rounds per level","aoe":"The illusionist","components":"V, S","ct":"2 segments","save":"None","save_type":"","description":"Alter Self\n\nSchool: Alteration/Illusion\nLevel: 2\nComponents: V, S\nRange: 0\nCasting Time: 2 segments\nDuration: 3d4 rounds + 2 rounds per level\nSaving Throw: None\nArea of Effect: The illusionist\nThis spell is similar to change self, but the alteration is quasi-real. The caster’s size can change by up to 50%. If the assumed form has wings, the illusionist may fly at one-quarter the true creature’s speed and with two worse Maneuverability Classes, to a minimum of E. If the form has gills, the caster can breathe underwater. Larger forms do not grant extra attacks or damage unless the illusionist is accustomed to that form.","notes":"","link":"","select_value":"Illusionist: Alter Self","class":"Illusionist"},"alter self":{"name":"Alter Self","level":"2","school":"Alteration/Illusion","range":"0","duration":"3d4 rounds + 2 rounds per level","aoe":"The illusionist","components":"V, S","ct":"2 segments","save":"None","save_type":"","descriptio