":"5","school":"Illusion/Phantasm","range":"1”","duration":"1 round per level","aoe":"Special","components":"S","ct":"2 segments","save":"None","save_type":"","description":"Shadow Door\n\nSchool: Illusion/Phantasm\nLevel: 5\nComponents: S\nRange: 1”\nCasting Time: 2 segments\nDuration: 1 round per level\nSaving Throw: None\nArea of Effect: Special\nThis spell creates the illusion of a door. It also allows the illusionist to appear to step through the door and disappear, when in reality the illusionist has darted aside and can then flee totally invisible for the spell’s duration. Creatures viewing the effect are deluded into seeing or entering an empty 10’ × 10’ room if they open the door. Only true seeing, a gem of seeing, or similar magical means reveal the illusionist.","notes":"","link":"","select_value":"Illusionist: Shadow Door","class":"Illusionist"},"shadow door":{"name":"Shadow Door","level":"5","school":"Illusion/Phantasm","range":"1”","duration":"1 round per level","aoe":"Special","components":"S","ct":"2 segments","save":"None","save_type":"","description":"Shadow Door\n\nSchool: Illusion/Phantasm\nLevel: 5\nComponents: S\nRange: 1”\nCasting Time: 2 segments\nDuration: 1 round per level\nSaving Throw: None\nArea of Effect: Special\nThis spell creates the illusion of a door. It also allows the illusionist to appear to step through the door and disappear, when in reality the illusionist has darted aside and can then flee totally invisible for the spell’s duration. Creatures viewing the effect are deluded into seeing or entering an empty 10’ × 10’ room if they open the door. Only true seeing, a gem of seeing, or similar magical means reveal the illusionist.","notes":"","link":"","class":"Illusionist"},"illusionist shadow magic":{"name":"Shadow Magic","level":"5","school":"Illusion/Phantasm","range":"5” + 1” per level","duration":"Special","aoe":"Special","components":"V, S","ct":"5 segments","save":"Special","save_type":"","description":"Shadow Magic\n\nSchool: Illusion/Phantasm\nLevel: 5\nComponents: V, S\nRange: 5” + 1” per level\nCasting Time: 5 segments\nDuration: Special\nSaving Throw: Special\nArea of Effect: Special\nThis spell allows the illusionist to cast a quasi-real magic-user spell. The spell can duplicate magic missile, fireball, lightning bolt, or cone of cold. It has normal effects on creatures in the area of effect if they fail their saving throws. If saving throws are made, the shadow magic effect deals only 1 hit point of damage per illusionist level, regardless of which quasi-real spell was cast.","notes":"","link":"","select_value":"Illusionist: Shadow Magic","class":"Illusionist"},"shadow magic":{"name":"Shadow Magic","level":"5","school":"Illusion/Phantasm","range":"5” + 1” per level","duration":"Special","aoe":"Special","components":"V, S","ct":"5 segments","save":"Special","save_type":"","description":"Shadow Magic\n\nSchool: Illusion/Phantasm\nLevel: 5\nComponents: V, S\nRange: 5” + 1” per level\nCasting Time: 5 segments\nDuration: Special\nSaving Throw: Special\nArea of Effect: Special\nThis spell allows the illusionist to cast a quasi-real magic-user spell. The spell can duplicate magic missile, fireball, lightning bolt, or cone of cold. It has normal effects on creatures in the area of effect if they fail their saving throws. If saving throws are made, the shadow magic effect deals only 1 hit point of damage per illusionist level, regardless of which quasi-real spell was cast.","notes":"","link":"","class":"Illusionist"},"illusionist summon shadow":{"name":"Summon Shadow","level":"5","school":"Conjuration/Summoning","range":"1”","duration":"1 round + 1 round per level","aoe":"1” × 1”","components":"V, S, M","ct":"5 segments","save":"None","save_type":"","description":"Summon Shadow\n\nSchool: Conjuration/Summoning\nLevel: 5\nComponents: V, S, M\nRange: 1”\nCasting Time: 5 segments\nDuration: 1 round + 1 round per level\nSaving Throw: None\nArea of Effect: 1” × 1”\nThis spell conjures 1 shadow for every 3 levels of experience the illusionist has attained. These shadows are under the illusionist’s control and attack the caster’s enemies on command. The shadows remain until slain, turned, or until the spell duration expires. Material Component: A bit of smoky quartz.","notes":"","link":"","select_value":"Illusionist: Summon Shadow","class":"Illusionist"},"summon shadow":{"name":"Summon Shadow","level":"5","school":"Conjuration/Summoning","range":"1”","duration":"1 round + 1 round per level","aoe":"1” × 1”","components":"V, S, M","ct":"5 segments","save":"None","save_type":"","description":"Summon Shadow\n\nSchool: Conjuration/Summoning\nLevel: 5\nComponents: V, S, M\nRange: 1”\nCasting Time: 5 segments\nDuration: 1 round + 1 round per level\nSaving Throw: None\nArea of Effect: 1” × 1”\nThis spell conjures 1 shadow for every 3 levels of experience the illusionist has attained. These shadows are under the illusionist’s control and attack the caster’s enemies on command. The shadows remain until slain, turned, or until the spell duration expires. Material Component: A bit of smoky quartz.","notes":"","link":"","class":"Illusionist"},"illusionist conjure animals":{"name":"Conjure Animals","level":"6","school":"Conjuration/Summoning","range":"3”","duration":"1 round per level","aoe":"Special","components":"V, S","ct":"6 segments","save":"None","save_type":"","description":"Conjure Animals\n\nSchool: Conjuration/Summoning\nLevel: 6\nComponents: V, S\nRange: 3”\nCasting Time: 6 segments\nDuration: 1 round per level\nSaving Throw: None\nArea of Effect: Special\nExcept as noted above, this spell is the same as the 6th-level cleric spell conjure animals.","notes":"","link":"","select_value":"Illusionist: Conjure Animals","class":"Illusionist"},"illusionist demi-shadow magic":{"name":"Demi-Shadow Magic","level":"6","school":"Illusion/Phantasm","range":"6” + 1” per level","duration":"Special","aoe":"Special","components":"V, S","ct":"6 segments","save":"Special","s